      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition, reflecting a standard of maintenance that is nothing short of exemplary. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior appointments, serves as a testament to its singular ownership history and sheltered life. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this offering represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector who demands absolute excellence in their acquisition.",
