    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece for the discerning collector: a vehicle that can only be described as being in showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Every panel gap is factory-perfect, and the trim remains dark and supple. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the high-grade leather upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the interior still carries that unmistakable scent of a brand-new vehicle. All electronics, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, function with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road debris or oxidation. This sale includes the full service history, original window sticker, two sets of keys, and all factory manuals. If you are looking for the finest example on the market, your search ends here.",
      "price": 48500.0,
